{"article_id":"UYCQ6gyDTTE35Uew","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The nuclear summit between President Trump and North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un fell apart Thursday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"when the parties failed to reach a deal over the issue of sanctions relief .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"In a news conference Trump explained","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"the meeting ended abruptly","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"because of Kim 's insistence","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"on lifting sanctions","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"without committing to the elimination of his country 's nuclear arsenal .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" I am always prepared to walk , \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"\" I am never afraid to walk from a deal . \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" I ' d much rather do it right","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"than do it fast , \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" We ' re in position","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to do something very special . \"","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that Mr. Kim was prepared to dismantle the North ' s Yongbyon nuclear complex , the site of a reactor and plutonium-reprocessing facility ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"if sanctions were lifted .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Washington wanted a deal","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to include other parts of the North ' s nuclear program ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"including undeclared sites","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"for producing highly enriched uranium .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"\" Basically , they wanted the sanctions lifted in their entirety","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and we couldn ' t do that , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"\" I just felt","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"it wasn ' t good enough , \"","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Mr. Trump said of the Yongbyon offer .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"\" We had to have more. \" [ ... ]","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Earlier , Mr. Trump told reporters","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"that he wasn ' t in a hurry","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"to reach a deal","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"as long as North Korea didn ' t conduct nuclear and missile tests ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"and asserted","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"he was optimistic","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that an accord","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"to denuclearize the peninsula","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"would eventually come .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"In front of the cameras earlier in the day , the two leaders appeared friendly ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"exchanging pleasantries ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"with Mr. Trump predicting","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that \" no matter what happens ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"we ' ll ultimately have a deal","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that ' s really good for Chairman Kim and his country. \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"But he added :","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" It doesn ' t mean we ' re doing it in one day , in one meeting. \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Kim , too , had sounded an upbeat note .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Asked by an American reporter","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"if he was willing to denuclearize ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Kim replied :","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" If I ' m not willing to do that ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"I wouldn ' t have come here. \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"( WSJ )","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"There was also some common ground on the issue","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"of whether the U.S. might open a liaison office in North Korea","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"-- a question","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"asked of both leaders by a reporter .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Trump called","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"it `` not a bad idea ''","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"while Kim said","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"it would be `` welcomable . ''","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"President @ realDonaldTrump and @ SecPompeo participate in a Press Conference in Hanoi , Vietnam , on February 28 , 2019.","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"pic.twitter.com/qgKX4cbuMd","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"-","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"Department of State","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"( @ StateDept )","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"February 28 , 2019","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"THANK YOU to our generous hosts in Hanoi this week :","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"President Trong , Prime Minister Phuc , and the wonderful people of Vietnam !","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"pic.twitter.com/AMqF0dfRhP","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"February 28 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"The two were expected to sign a joint agreement Thursday afternoon ,","depth":3},{"id":75,"text":"but that ceremony was cancelled along with a scheduled lunch meeting .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":137,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":105,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":82,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":77,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":78,"right":80,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":80,"left":4,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":89,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":87,"right":88,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":84,"right":86,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":83,"right":9,"relatio